    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h1",
          "text": "A Leading Popcorn Producer Implements Folio3 IntelliFabric Dashboards Suite"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Overcome complex data and analytics challenges and maximize ROI with IntelliFabric, Folio3's Azure-powered solution built on Microsoft Fabric."
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "CONTACT US TO MODERNIZE YOUR FARM",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/weaver-popcorn-hybrids.webp",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 761,
          "h": 626
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Home » Case Studies » Popcorn Producer Intellifabric Dashboards"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Indiana, United States"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Farming and Seed Production"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "11–50 employees"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Weaver Popcorn Hybrids"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "About The Client",
        "Our client is a leading producer of popcorn hybrids, operating at scale across global production and distribution. With deep expertise in seed development and a long-standing position in the popcorn industry, the company manages a complex operational footprint — from agronomy and production planning to inventory, sales, and global distribution.\nThat complexity demanded a robust analytics layer capable of turning raw ERP data into actionable business intelligence. The leadership team needed a single, reliable source of truth — not another report waiting to be built."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Delayed Insights and Reactive Decision-Making"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Key business areas impacted included:"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Financial performance visibility"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Sales and revenue analysis"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inventory and operational oversight"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The client's core operational data lived in Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central, but converting that data into timely, actionable insights had become a bottleneck. Reporting was heavily manual, which meant leadership was always looking at yesterday's picture of the business — never today's.\nThe downstream effects were felt across three critical areas:",
        "The cumulative effect was the same one many growing manufacturers face: decision-making that relied on delayed, fragmented, and static reports rather than real-time, insight-driven analytics."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "FACING SIMILAR CHALLENGES?",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "One Source of Truth, Powered by IntelliFabric"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 deployed its IntelliFabric Solution — a purpose-built analytics offering designed for seamless integration with Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central, built on Azure and Microsoft Fabric.\nThe solution established a secure, direct connection to the client's Business Central environment and t"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Secure integration with Dynamics 365 Business Central"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Automated data extraction and transformation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Pre-built Finance, Sales, and Inventory dashboards"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Real-time KPI tracking against budget and history"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Unified, single view of business performance"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Interactive and visual analytics"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Scalable analytics foundation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Elimination of manual reporting effort"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "TRANSFORM YOUR GROWER DATA",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Key Features"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Financial Performance Monitoring"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Income & Balance Sheet Overview"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Profitability Metrics"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Liquidity Ratios"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Expense Analysis"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Sales and Customer Insights"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Sales Performance Tracking"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Budget Comparison"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Detailed Analysis"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inventory and Cost Management"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inventory Valuation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "COGS Tracking"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The Business Central Dashboards Suite delivered three core capability sets, each addressing a specific area of operational oversight.",
        "Provided immediate visibility into key financial statements.",
        "Tracked Gross Profit (USD) and Net Profit (USD) with Year-over-Year (YoY) comparisons for quick performance assessment",
        "Displayed vital metrics like the Current Ratio and Quick Ratio for instantaneous financial health checks.",
        "Broke down Total Expenses by category (Facility, Management, Banking, etc.) and provided Budget vs. Actual comparisons.",
        "Monitored metrics such as Sales (USD) FYOYTD and Adjusted Profit (%).",
        "Visualized monthly and departmental Sales vs. Budget trends.",
        "Allowed deep dives into performance by specific Customer and Salesperson",
        "Categorized and tracked Inventory Value by Aging Group and Item Category for efficient stock management.",
        "Monitored Cost of Goods Sold (COGS) in relation to Inventory Value to manage costs."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "Achieve These With Copilot",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        },
        {
          "text": "Achieve These With Copilot",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        },
        {
          "text": "Achieve These With Copilot",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
